  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Parliament ends its term",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliament (the second session of the Ninth Parliament) was adjourned today (28) from midnight.",
        "As indicated in the gazette announcement, the parliament which has ended its term will be ceremonially reopened by the President on Wednesday, the 3rd of next month.",
        "After ceremonially opening the Parliament, President Ranil Wickremesinghe will present his manifesto.",
        "A parliamentary official said that after a new president is appointed, it is a common tradition to open the parliament at the end of the term.",
        "With the end of the term of Parliament, more than 50 committees, including CoP, Copa, were abolished. In order for those committees to become active, their members must be appointed and re-established."
      ],
